\f0\b\fs52 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 Part 1: Automated Audio Transitions (Sound Design)\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 To make your 6-hour video sound completely immersive, the background ambient noise (the "foley") should change based on the mall\'92s opening hours. We can do this without relying on complex audio editing software by utilizing 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 FFmpeg's complex audio filtergraphs
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  to layer your music with dynamic background ambiance.\
