\f0\b\fs42 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 The Soundscape Setup\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 Prepare three distinct audio files in your main project directory:\
\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 \cf0 {\listtext	1.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 lofi_music.mp3 \'96 Your endless, continuous background instrumental tracks.\
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 {\listtext	2.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 mall_day_ambiance.mp3 \'96 Subtle, echoey sounds of a populated mall (distant footsteps, faint chatter, air conditioning hum).\
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 {\listtext	3.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 mall_night_ambiance.mp3 \'96 Deep, hollow echoes, isolated building hums, creaking structures, or occasional distant water droplets.\
